('Sara', 'Sometimes .Net, sometimes Express, sometimes Next. Next can be good esp for smaller teams or solo devs since you can do backend/frontend all on server side, but it is fairly opinionated and has its own quirks.', '2015-09-01T13:10:00Z', 6, 'https://cdn.sanity.io/images/3do82whm/next/4b1f008289a88f4438a1c983fb32cf1a636d9d0e-1000x667.png?w=720&h=480&fit=clip&auto=format');